<title>USA: Salomon Bros names Lachman to emerging market post.</title>
<headline>Salomon Bros names Lachman to emerging market post.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-09-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Salomon Brothers Inc said they named Desmond Lachman as global coordinator for emerging market economic research.</p>
<p>In this newly created position, Lachman will be responsible for formulating the firm's overall strategic view of emerging markets in conjunction with the team of area and country specialists.</p>
<p>Lachman came to Salomon from the International Monetary Fund where most recently he was deputy director of the Policy Development and Review Department.</p>
<p>--NA Treasury Deak, 212-859-1674</p>
